---
import WidgetLayout from '../../layouts/WidgetLayout.astro';
---
<WidgetLayout title="ListBox">
  <h1>ListBox</h1>
  <p>Scrollable selection list.</p>

  <h2>Preview</h2>
  <pre class="ascii-mockup">┌────────────────────────────┐   <span class="focused">╭────────────────────────────╮</span>
│  Iron Legion               │   <span class="focused">│</span>  Iron Legion               <span class="focused">│</span>
│  Crimson Horde             │   <span class="focused">│</span>▸ Crimson Horde             <span class="focused">│</span>
│  Starborn                  │   <span class="focused">│</span>  Starborn                  <span class="focused">│</span>
│  Void Reapers              │   <span class="focused">│</span>  Void Reapers              <span class="focused">│</span>
└────────────────────────────┘   <span class="focused">╰────────────────────────────╯</span>
 unfocused                        focused (rounded, primary)</pre>

  <h2>Accessible mode</h2>
  <pre class="ascii-mockup">Faction: Crimson Horde
  1. Iron Legion
  2. Crimson Horde (selected)
  3. Starborn</pre>

  <h2>Props</h2>
  <table>
    <thead><tr><th>Prop</th><th>Type</th><th>Notes</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>value</td><td>string</td><td></td></tr>
      <tr><td>onChange</td><td>function</td><td></td></tr>
      <tr><td>options</td><td><code>{"{ value, label }[]"}</code></td><td></td></tr>
      <tr><td>height</td><td>number?</td><td>default 4</td></tr>
      <tr><td>disabled</td><td>boolean?</td><td></td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>Type-to-filter composition</h2>
  <p>For type-to-filter, compose <code>useFilter</code> + <code>TextField</code> + <code>ListBox</code>:</p>
  <pre><code>const filter = useFilter(options);
&lt;TextField value={'{'}filter.text{'}'} onChange={'{'}filter.setText{'}'} /&gt;
&lt;ListBox options={'{'}filter.filtered{'}'} value={'{'}value{'}'} onChange={'{'}onChange{'}'} /&gt;</code></pre>

  <h2>Interactive demo</h2>
  <div class="demo-placeholder">Interactive demo coming soon</div>
</WidgetLayout>
